Chilean Police Chief Gordon Submits Resignation to President

-- B y   R a n d y   W o o d s
-- 
2011-09-02T16:25:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/chilean-police-chief-gordon-submits-resignation-to-president.html
Chile ’s police chief, General
Eduardo Gordon, submitted his resignation to President Sebastian Pinera following accusations that he intervened to protect his
son from charges related to a car accident.  Gordon’s comments were carried live by state-owned
television channel TVN. He denied the accusations.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Joshua Goodman  at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 